Padre - Perl Application Development and Refactoring Environment

A Perl IDE and general-purpose editor using WxWidgets.

Installation:

Alien::WxWidgets
Wx
Padre

For detailed installation instructions look at 

http://padre.perlide.org/wiki/Download

